{{Infobox video game | title = Dream PetHouse | image = | caption = | developer = [[Zynga]] | publisher = Zynga | composer = | release = February 2, 2012 | genre = [[Simulation video game]] | modes = | platforms = [[iOS]], [[Android (operating system)|Android]] }} '''''Dream PetHouse''''' was a [[Mobile_game|mobile]] [[Simulation_video_game|simulation]] [[social network game]] created by [[Zynga]]. This game was available for users to download starting on February 2, 2012.<ref>{{cite web|title=Zynga officially launches Dream PetHouse|url=http://www.insidemobileapps.com/2012/02/02/zynga-officially-launches-dream-pethouse-but-stays-quiet-on-dream-heights/|publisher=insidemobileapps.com|accessdate=22 May 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Lofte|first=Leanna|title=Create a massive home for hundreds of pets in Dream PetHouse by Zynga|url=http://www.imore.com/create-massive-home-hundreds-pets-dream-pethouse-zynga|publisher=imore.com|accessdate=22 May 2013}}</ref> The game was similar to other games that focus on building, such as Zynga ''Dream Zoo''. In the ''Dream PetHouse'' game, users could collect and care for cute, adorable animals.<ref>{{cite web|title=iTunes Preview: Dream PetHouse by Zynga|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dream-pethouse/id485164994?mt=8|publisher=iTunes|accessdate=22 May 2013}}</ref> A free version of the game was available to users, but to speed up his or her advancement in the game, a user could pay real money to buy digital fruit, seeds or coins.<ref>{{cite web|title=Dream PetHouse Overview|url=http://www.gamezebo.com/games/dream-pethouse|publisher=gamezebo.com|accessdate=22 May 2013}}</ref> This type of game is known as a [[freemium]]. The height of Dream PetHouse's popularity was in June, 2012, when according to [[Daily_Active_Users|Daily Active User (DAU)]] metrics, there were about 400,515 daily users.<ref name="appmtr">{{cite web|title=Dream PetHouse by Zynga|url=http://www.appmtr.com/facebook/app/244029685655631-dream-pethouse/|publisher=appmtr.com|accessdate=22 May 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130628105255/http://www.appmtr.com/facebook/app/244029685655631-dream-pethouse/|archivedate=28 June 2013|df=}}</ref> Using DAU metrics, ''Dream PetHouse'' had about 12,602 daily users in April, 2013.<ref name="appmtr" /> Beginning in May 21, 2013, Zynga announced that it would cease supporting this game on June 28, 2013. The game was supposed to be shut down on June 28; the server was finally shut down on July 4 or 5.<ref>{{cite web|title=Greetings Pethouse Players|url=https://www.facebook.com/DreamPetHouse|publisher=Zynga|accessdate=22 May 2013}}</ref>
